snippet.title: Welcome to The Arcade! Soon in America
snippet.description:
Sign up for American users:
https://www.portalone.com/playtime

Discover a brand new mobile gaming entertainment experience... where everyone has a chance to win real prizes! 
We are releasing to the US in August and by signing up now and inviting your friends, you're part of a draw to win big prizes!

Be one of the first to ever play in the PortalOne Arcade in the US by signing up! 

Norwegian app download:
iPhone: https://apps.apple.com/no/app/portalone-arcade-norway/id1495839430?fbclid=IwAR2fgNPY-lWTSxlyuYuG3CthNHf6wkp8qungO0V0Efw4YsnFh1dgegZZtEM
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.portalone.arcade&fbclid=IwAR329jeC-9ZPKuRpo1BkXMvI4HQSgwYHsWwKLjJnQWATqOmOXtosKtXuo_Q
